						<summary>

						<p>This is dated the <hi rend="bold">10th year</hi> of the reign of the Yādava king <hi rend="bold">Rāmachandradēva,</hi> cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Pramāthi, Phālguṇa, śu. 11, Sōmavāra</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1280 February 12, Monday.</hi> It records the grant by the <hi rend="italic">Rājaguru</hi> <hi rend="bold">Vubhaṇayitavāhi-Dēvarāṇeya</hi> of <hi rend="italic">gadyāṇas</hi> 8 to the 12 <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Beṇṇeyahaḷḷi</hi> and 2 <hi rend="italic">mattars</hi> to <hi rend="bold">Kalajīya</hi> on account of the charity of <hi rend="bold">Ramābāyi</hi> for a water-shed in the <hi rend="italic">samthe.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
